headline: Keurig Dr Pepper Announces Secondary Offering of Common Stock by JAB
summary: Keurig Dr Pepper (NASDAQ: KDP) (the "Company" or "KDP") announced today that a subsidiary of JAB Holding Company s.a.r.l. ("JAB") will sell an aggregate of 75,000,000 shares of KDP common stock through a proposed registered public offering.
